  <brief_title>Study of Efficacy and Safety of Ginger Extract Compared With Loratadine for Treatment of Allergic Rhinitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Study of Efficacy and Adverse Effects of Ginger Extract and Loratadine for Treatment of Allergic Rhinitis Patients (Clinical Trial Phase II)</official_title>
