  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Efficacy and adverse effects of Ginger extract in treating allergic rhinitis patients
      compared with Loratadine.The double blind randomized controlled trial study was approved by
      the Human Research Ethics Committee of Thammasat University NO.1.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The double blind randomized controlled trial study. Patients who meet the inclusion criteria
      and do not fall into any exclusion criteria will be randomly placed into the experimental
      group, who will receive ginger extract capsules, or the control group, who will receive
      loratadine for 42 days.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
